Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:46.28,Song-ENG [720p],,0,0,0,,Gently devours you, body and soul
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:46.28,Song-JAP [720p],,0,0,0,,Yasashiku hamu wa anata no subete o
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.19,0:20:51.03,ED JP-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur3\fad(150,150)}It's my guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.49,0:20:51.45,Song-ENG [720p],,0,0,0,,It's my guilty
