Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:11.97,Song-ENG [720p],,0,0,0,,Call my name and give me a kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:14.32,ED JP-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}そして抱きしめて
