Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.07,0:21:28.16,Song-JAP [720p],,0,0,0,,Mada katachi o nokoshiteiru wa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.37,0:21:33.75,Song-ENG [720p],,0,0,0,,I glimpse a vivid red eternity
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.37,0:21:33.75,Song-JAP [720p],,0,0,0,,Akaku azayaka na eien ga miete
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:33.63,ED JP-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}鮮やかな永遠が見えて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.63,0:21:37.71,ED JP-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}隣でそれは歌いだすわ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.95,0:21:35.92,Song-ENG [720p],,0,0,0,,It starts singing right next to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.95,0:21:35.92,Song-JAP [720p],,0,0,0,,Tonari de sore wa utaidasu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:41.13,Song-ENG [720p],,0,0,0,,What was I born for
